#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Attaching Files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Attachment Methods"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:5
msgid ""
"Attach a file by drag and drop or by clicking the attachment icon in the "
"message input box."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:8
msgid ""
"Upload a file or selection of files by dragging the files from your "
"computer into the RHS or center pane. Dragging and dropping attaches the "
"files to the message input box, then you can optionally type a message "
"and press ENTER to post."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Attachment Icon"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:11
msgid ""
"Alternatively, upload files by clicking the grey paperclip icon inside "
"the message input box. This opens up your system file viewer where you "
"can navigate to the desired files and then click Open to upload the files"
" to the message input box. Optionally type a message and then press ENTER"
" to post."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "File Previewer"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:14
msgid ""
"Mattermost has a built in file previewer that is used to view media, "
"download files and share public links. Click the thumbnail of an attached"
" file to open it in the file previewer."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Sharing Public Links"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:18
msgid ""
"Public links allow you to share file attachments with people outside your"
" Mattermost team. Open the file previewer by clicking on the thumbnail of"
" an attachment, then click Get Public Link. The file will open in a new "
"browser tab and the redirect URL can be shared with anyone. Public links "
"expire after a period of time and become inaccessible for security "
"reasons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:20
msgid ""
"If Get Public Link is not visible in the file previewer then contact your"
" system administrator to enable public file links in the System Console "
"file settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Downloading Files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:24
msgid ""
"Download an attached file by clicking the download icon next to the file "
"thumbnail or by opening the file previewer and clicking Download."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "Supported Media Types"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:27
msgid ""
"If you are trying to preview a media type that is not supported, the file"
" previewer will open a standard media attachment icon. Supported media "
"formats depend heavily on your browser and operating system, but the "
"following formats are supported by Mattermost on most browsers:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:29
msgid "Images: BMP, GIF, JPG, JPEG, PNGVideo: MP4Audio: MP3, M4A"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:33
msgid "Document preview (PDF, Word, Excel, PPT) is not yet supported."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md
msgid "File Size Limitations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/messaging/attaching-files.md:36
msgid ""
"Mattermost supports a maximum of five attached files per post, each with "
"a maximum file size of 50Mb."
msgstr ""

